{"tid":1356314,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"石鏡泉完美示範退而不休 繼續為經濟日報寫專欄","createTime":"2019-07-23T13:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T08:03:52.000Z","uid":88070,"like":76,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3bedd30759371bab62bec10c8d269e5f30721729","tid":1356314,"uid":88070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QN8f1HA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQN8f1HA.png&h=78449ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n石鏡泉先生 (「石先生」) 因<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有意從事於彼之其他個人興趣</span></span>，於二零一九年七月二十二日向董事會提出<span style=\"color: red;\">辭任</span>本公司執行董事及本 集團刊物香港經濟日報副社長，董事會於二零一九年七月二十三日批准並即時 生效。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">石先生將繼續為本集團專欄作家。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n永久抵制經濟日報集團行動繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2019/0723/ltn20190723581_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkexnews.hk%2Flistedco%2Flistconews%2Fsehk%2F2019%2F0723%2Fltn20190723581_c.pdf&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4f1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=ab355ec9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2019/0723/ltn20190723581_c.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"88ffa6fb32a62085a9ff2d494245f6ecc12ab377","tid":1356314,"uid":79456,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:01:52.000Z","msg":"經濟日報<br />\nU magazine<br />\nEzone <br />\nIMoney<br />\n<br />\n仲有啲咩"},{"pid":"1ef275fc7abb4f293440562145f5002ca901f136","tid":1356314,"uid":88070,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:03:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全面抵制經濟日報及旗下媒體</span></span><br />\n<br />\n媒體業務<br />\n香港經濟日報 <a href=\"http://hket.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhket.